{"type":"message","id":"ac316343","parentId":"b3cf90e6","timestamp":"2026-02-17T19:42:50.455Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-17 21:42 GMT+2] OS-AGNOSTIC BROADCAST, ERROR COLLECTION & ROADMAP V6.\n\n1.  **Fix Broadcaster (`scripts/broadcast_log.py`):**\n    *   *Logic:* Use `pathlib` and standard file reading. No grep.\n    *   *Filter:* Python list comprehension `if any(level in line for level in ['ERROR', 'WARN', ...])`.\n    *   *Auth:* `from dotenv import load_dotenv; load_dotenv()`.\n\n2.  **Blacklist Collection:**\n    *   *Scan:* Read `logs/*.log` and `docs/FINAL_AUDIT_REPORT.md`.\n    *   *Extract:* All negative lines.\n    *   *Save:* `reports/THE_NAKED_TRUTH.txt`.\n\n3.  **Roadmap v6 (`docs/ROADMAP_V6.md`):**\n    *   Phase 1: Windows Native (Pathlib, No-Bash).\n    *   Phase 2: Iron Core (Rust DLLs).\n    *   Phase 3: Cloud Mind (Redis Cloud).\n\n4.  **Execute Broadcast:**\n    *   Run `python scripts/broadcast_log.py reports/THE_NAKED_TRUTH.txt`.\n    *   Run `python scripts/broadcast_log.py docs/ROADMAP_V6.md`.\n\n5.  **Sleep Signal:**\n    *   Send \"😴 System Standby\"."}],"timestamp":1771357370453}}
